Kill the traitor!

00:01:10.720 --> 00:01:11.480
Traitor!

00:01:11.840 --> 00:01:12.799
Traitor!

00:01:13.159 --> 00:01:14.079
Traitor!

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:14.920
Traitor!

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:15.799
Kill him!

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:17.680
I regret...

00:01:18.560 --> 00:01:19.439
I hate...

00:01:20.120 --> 00:01:21.000
Why didn't I

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:23.519
just run you through with my sword?

00:01:24.640 --> 00:01:25.840
Then the throne

00:01:27.120 --> 00:01:28.680
would have belonged to the Huo family.

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.760
You once said,

00:01:32.448 --> 00:01:34.272
"Hunting boars requires
three-edged arrows."

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:48.519
The pupil has surpassed the master.

00:01:49.359 --> 00:01:51.719
I learned well.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:56.879
Even if I die,

00:01:57.200 --> 00:01:58.319
my soul will endure.

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:02.319
Even if I go to the underworld,

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:03.799
I will see,

00:02:04.599 --> 00:02:05.359
Chen Yu,

00:02:05.799 --> 00:02:08.919
how you ruin this empire.

00:02:12.360 --> 00:02:13.879
This final game,

00:02:15.479 --> 00:02:17.039
you've lost to me.

00:02:18.319 --> 00:02:19.439
Do you know

00:02:20.479 --> 00:02:22.360
the most exquisite part

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:27.319
is that the wolf cub you raised

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:29.919
is now gnawing

00:02:32.120 --> 00:02:33.719
on the last bone.

00:02:39.960 --> 00:02:40.719
My son,

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:44.319
today is your grandfather's...

00:02:47.639 --> 00:02:48.280
No.

00:02:49.520 --> 00:02:52.599
Today is the day traitor Huo Chengxuan
meets his fate.

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:56.039
Your Highness, the Chancellor...

00:03:01.520 --> 00:03:02.080
Father,

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.719
when teaching me chess, you told me

00:03:06.400 --> 00:03:07.680
to sacrifice pieces quickly

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:09.520
and ruthlessly.

00:03:11.479 --> 00:03:12.680
Did it ever cross your mind

00:03:14.319 --> 00:03:15.280
that one day,

00:03:16.639 --> 00:03:18.280
the biggest sacrificial piece

00:03:20.039 --> 00:03:21.719
would be you?

00:03:27.879 --> 00:03:28.719
My son,

00:03:29.919 --> 00:03:31.000
remember this day.

00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:33.479
The deadliest move in the world

00:03:35.919 --> 00:03:36.960
is family.

00:03:47.400 --> 00:03:48.000
Everyone,

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:50.520
the Grand Princess was wronged.

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:53.199
Luckily, His Majesty
uncovered the truth.

00:03:53.888 --> 00:03:55.120
The traitor stands condemned.

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:56.919
As a scion of the Sheng family,

00:03:58.400 --> 00:03:59.280
by imperial decree,

00:04:00.120 --> 00:04:01.159
I proclaim the charges.

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:05.199
Proclaim the charges.

00:04:06.599 --> 00:04:08.039
Traitor Huo Chengxuan

00:04:09.479 --> 00:04:10.879
showed no respect to heaven,

00:04:11.840 --> 00:04:13.319
and slaughtered common folk below.

00:04:14.719 --> 00:04:15.800
Holding high office,

00:04:16.839 --> 00:04:18.600
he should have served
his sovereign loyally.

00:04:19.680 --> 00:04:22.000
Yet he was consumed by desire,
committing grave crimes.

00:04:22.784 --> 00:04:24.032
In the third year of Jiahe,

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:27.560
driven by personal ambition,
he forged evidence,

00:04:29.800 --> 00:04:32.480
leading to the wrongful death
of the Grand Princess.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:35.480
First kowtow!

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:38.360
Plead for the Grand Princess!

00:04:38.560 --> 00:04:39.399
Kill him!

00:04:39.519 --> 00:04:40.600
Traitor!

00:04:40.920 --> 00:04:41.800
Treacherous minister!

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:43.040
Traitor!

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:43.800
Traitor!

00:04:43.959 --> 00:04:44.759
Kill him!

00:04:44.759 --> 00:04:46.439
Traitor Huo Chengxuan

00:04:46.439 --> 00:04:50.120
- Kill him!
- colluded with foreign enemies,

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:52.560
causing the loyal soldiers
of the Sheng army

00:04:53.279 --> 00:04:54.519
to die unjustly at the border.

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:57.920
Their bones lie cold, barely buried!

00:04:59.600 --> 00:05:00.959
Plead for the loyal martyrs

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:03.480
of the Sheng family.

00:05:04.199 --> 00:05:05.160
Second kowtow!

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:08.639
Plead for the loyal martyrs
of the Sheng family!

00:05:11.328 --> 00:05:12.352
Indeed.

00:05:12.352 --> 00:05:14.080
He's too evil to die just once.

00:05:14.920 --> 00:05:15.759
This is

00:05:16.800 --> 00:05:18.240
the battle standard stained

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:21.439
with the blood of 30,000 Sheng soldiers!

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:31.680
Here is the secret letter you wrote,

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:34.240
demanding King Liang send troops

00:05:34.480 --> 00:05:36.399
to lure the Sheng army into a trap

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:40.439
and massacre them all!

00:05:41.639 --> 00:05:42.920
His crimes demand death!

00:05:44.120 --> 00:05:44.720
Now,

00:05:45.560 --> 00:05:47.759
Chancellor Huo's crimes
are exposed to all.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.839
He shall be punished

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:52.600
to appease the people

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:55.480
and to honor the loyal souls.

00:05:57.160 --> 00:05:58.279
Three bows!

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.279
Plead for the people's suffering!

00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:09.759
His Majesty has arrived.

00:06:12.896 --> 00:06:15.357
(In Memory of Grand Princess,
Sheng Yunlin)

00:06:17.399 --> 00:06:18.160
Kneel properly!

00:06:23.480 --> 00:06:26.680
Welcome the tablet of Grand Princess,
Sheng Yunlin.

00:06:55.720 --> 00:06:56.360
Do it.

00:07:09.079 --> 00:07:11.360
Heaven has no eyes!

00:07:55.936 --> 00:07:56.959
Back then, Chancellor Huo

00:07:57.839 --> 00:07:59.279
colluded with the enemy state,

00:08:00.079 --> 00:08:03.360
causing thousands of Sheng men
to shed blood on the battlefield

00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:04.399
and die a dishonest death.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.519
He branded me a traitorous collaborator.

00:08:09.879 --> 00:08:12.439
Then he sent Su Wei
to kill in my Weiyang Palace.

00:08:13.152 --> 00:08:14.800
He ordered Huo Wan to burn the evidence.

00:08:16.839 --> 00:08:18.319
He schemed against me so thoroughly,

00:08:19.199 --> 00:08:20.360
but did he ever consider

00:08:21.240 --> 00:08:23.040
that today he'd be outmaneuvered
to death.

00:08:24.399 --> 00:08:27.120
The Sheng men were all loyal and brave.

00:08:28.199 --> 00:08:29.000
After so many years,

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:30.519
their names are finally cleared.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:34.759
Their unwavering devotion
was not in vain.

00:08:45.240 --> 00:08:45.960
Lord Xie,

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:50.159
aren't you usually the epitome
of composure?

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.080
Why are you so visibly elated today?

00:09:00.240 --> 00:09:01.399
I've discussed with Mother.

00:09:02.639 --> 00:09:03.879
Once all matters are settled,

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:07.320
I will prepare all necessary rites,

00:09:07.759 --> 00:09:09.279
and request you from the Sheng family.

00:09:13.159 --> 00:09:13.759
Then,

00:09:15.799 --> 00:09:18.720
with a proper, honorable wedding,

00:09:20.159 --> 00:09:21.559
I will bring you into my home.

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:24.120
I won't betray you.

00:09:26.440 --> 00:09:28.440
Rushing to marry in such a fluster?

00:09:29.320 --> 00:09:30.320
Aren't you ashamed?

00:09:39.279 --> 00:09:41.039
I want everyone under heaven to know

00:09:42.559 --> 00:09:43.600
that you are my wife.

00:10:40.960 --> 00:10:43.648
(Huo Wan)

00:11:04.200 --> 00:11:05.519
Xie the ice block,

00:11:06.279 --> 00:11:07.759
why so many vats in your house?

00:11:09.919 --> 00:11:11.039
Huaiyong isn't home.

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:12.720
Do I not exist to you?

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:21.440
My lady!

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:23.879
My lady!

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:25.200
You're finally back!

00:11:25.759 --> 00:11:26.879
I've waited so bitterly.

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:30.159
You climb over walls every day.

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:32.440
Lady Xie provides you with fine meals.

00:11:34.030 --> 00:11:35.000
Where's the bitterness?

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:36.399
My lady, you have no idea.

00:11:37.240 --> 00:11:38.080
God knows

00:11:38.120 --> 00:11:39.800
where Xie Fei got all those vats again

00:11:39.800 --> 00:11:40.960
and placed them by the wall.

00:11:41.320 --> 00:11:42.360
I thought there won't be

00:11:42.639 --> 00:11:44.559
any vats after I smashed them last time.

00:11:47.080 --> 00:11:47.720
Get away!

00:11:48.519 --> 00:11:50.639
Didn't stop you, the wall-scaling thief.

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:00.159
I truly don't know

00:12:01.056 --> 00:12:02.656
what's so great about Xie the ice block.

00:12:03.240 --> 00:12:04.360
He's born a workhorse.

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:07.519
My lady,

00:12:08.960 --> 00:12:10.159
- why not come with me?
- I...

00:12:11.159 --> 00:12:11.960
I heard

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:14.039
a new opera troupe came
to the southern city,

00:12:14.360 --> 00:12:15.159
by the temple fair.

00:12:15.440 --> 00:12:16.600
Let's go have fun together.

00:12:18.080 --> 00:12:18.960
You've now

00:12:19.799 --> 00:12:21.360
gotten so familiar with the capital.

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:23.080
My lady,

00:12:25.440 --> 00:12:26.480
look up at the sky.

00:12:32.039 --> 00:12:33.679
Don't you want to see

00:12:34.440 --> 00:12:36.559
what this land you fought for
will become?

00:12:45.039 --> 00:12:46.159
What Xie Fei can give you,

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.080
I can give you too.

00:12:49.799 --> 00:12:50.799
What he cannot give you,

00:12:52.279 --> 00:12:53.039
I also can.

00:12:59.080 --> 00:12:59.679
Are you willing

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:01.320
to be confined within this small grid,

00:13:02.799 --> 00:13:03.919
within the imperial city,

00:13:05.039 --> 00:13:05.960
as some fated lady?

00:13:08.600 --> 00:13:09.279
I am not willing.

00:13:24.039 --> 00:13:25.080
But Li Jingche,

00:13:26.360 --> 00:13:27.240
in this life,

00:13:29.279 --> 00:13:30.440
I will marry only Xie Fei.

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:40.000
Miss Sheng,

00:13:40.200 --> 00:13:41.919
